    "description": "Book a tour on a quad bike or in a 4x4 off-road vehicle. If you love zooming over uneven terrain on four wheels, a quad tour is just the thing for you. These vehicles are so nimble that you can conquer almost any terrain with ease. Exploring rugged landscapes is even more fun in a group, even if you don't have any prior quad experience. The only thing you need to bring is a valid driver's license. With a 4x4 off-road vehicle, you'll also enjoy driving off the beaten path. With robust technology and four-wheel drive, you'll tackle steep slopes and muddy tracks. Whether you're driving or riding shotgun, you'll find real adventure in the wilderness."
